domestic flights. china has many domestic flights connecting all the major cities and tourist destinations. airlines include the three international carriers: air china, china southern, and china eastern, as well as regional ones including hainan airlines, shenzhen airlines, sichuan airlines and shanghai airlines. in recent years, it has been popular for large cities and provinces to open their own (dubiously funded) airline. these include chongqing airlines, chengdu airline and hebei airlines, amongst others. the parent company behind hainan airlines has spawned some 13 airlines in the region, including grand china air, yangtse express, hong kong airlines and deer jet. flights 